## üîß **Technical Implementation**

### **Data Flow**
```
Frontend Form ‚Üí Google Apps Script ‚Üí Your Google Sheet
```

### **Request Configuration**
```javascript
// All forms now use this configuration:
const response = await fetch('https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbxKWCvfF8k5mWo3l5sSD9EiR0SfBCGnTI29RrAFknnFBH-wZ1MX7Al7tTVH_4dAI05qnw/exec', {
    method: 'POST',
    mode: 'cors',
    headers: {
        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        name: sanitizedData.name,
        email: sanitizedData.email,
        phone: sanitizedData.phone,
        message: sanitizedData.message,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent // Added automatically
    })
});
```

### **Response Handling**
```javascript
const result = await response.json();
if (result.result === 'success') {
    // Show success message and reset form
    setSubmitStatus({
        type: 'success',
        message: 'Thank you! Your message has been sent successfully.'
    });
} else {
    // Handle error
    throw new Error(result.error || 'Submission failed');
}
```

