## üîç **What Gets Saved to Your Google Sheet**

Each form submission saves the following data:

| **Field** | **Description** | **Example** |
|-----------|----------------|-------------|
| `name` | User's full name | "John Doe" |
| `email` | Email address | "john@example.com" |
| `phone` | Phone number | "9876543210" |
| `message` | Contact message | "I want to know about..." |
| `userAgent` | Browser/device info | Automatically added |

